snippet.title: Doki Doki Ragnarok - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Pillage, conquer, chat and flirt with villages all over the world in this historically accurate viking adventure.
Play now in Early Access: http://DokiDokiRagnarok.com

Available on itch.io. Other platforms (including Steam) will follow.
